	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Tricks Of The Trade</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_HELP">
			<Text>Merchants courted by our Foreign Advisor have learned of the trade routes to our City, and are interested in investing in local business.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Trade at the Caravansary produces +3 [ICON_GOLD] Gold.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Our prestigious hunters collect pelts and hides that would sell well abroad.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Trade at the Caravansary produces +3 [ICON_FOOD] Food.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Plantations around the City are home to fruit that will not grow in foreign lands.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Trade at the Lighthouse produces +2 [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Our fishing industry can transport heavy equipment and materials long distances with ease, a capability these foreigners do not have access to.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Trade at the Caravansary produces +2 [ICON_CULTURE] culture.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_CITY_EVENT_AES_FOREIGN_CITY_GOOD_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Our large scale excavations produce huge amounts of a handsome stone that is in high demand with their artists.</Text>
		</Row>
